byline.original: By MICHAEL J. de la MERCED

abstract: DealBook Online; New York real estate dynasty scions Jared and Joshua Kushner have founded start-up Cadre, which has raised more than $18.3 million.
lead_paragraph: Their start-up, Cadre, which aims to make it easier for select clients to invest in real estate, has raised more than $18.3 million.

headline.main: Kushner Brothers Combine Real Estate and Technology
